<br>
1) All mana generated from buffs is DPS gained. If you are 100% mana you will not regenerate any more mana and this dps is suddenly being shot off into space.<br>
<br>
2) Harvests and rods give you mana when you use them! The earlier you use one, the more likely you'll get to refresh it. For instance, 12 fight you pop rod at 30 seconds, then at 5min 30 seconds, then at 10min 30 seconds. If you wait for 20% of the fight you pop rod 2 min 24 sec later. I'll say 2 nukes for the rod and you pop it at 2 min 39 sec, 7 min 39 sec... and oh it's dead by the time you get the next rod off<br>
<br>
3) You should be under your tank's aggro/sec level by a bit, so that whether you start nuking at 99% or 80%, you won't get summoned(so long as he lives).<br>
<br>
